text = "Welcome to the Project: Unknown prototype!


Controls:
WASD - to move
E - interact(to interact with the ladder and bunker hatch)
Escape - to open up the pause menu
NOTE: THERE IS NO SAVE SYSTEM IN THIS VERSION. 
PRESSING THE MAIN MENU BUTTON WILL REQUIRE YOU TO MAKE A NEW GAME.
NOTHING YOU DO WILL SAVE!!

I hope you enjoy my prototype and please give me ANY feedback about the game!!"
